full_text: Read more about my bill, the Overtime Reform and Enhancement Act at https://t.co/PRJYxqrJno
My bill will immediately increase the #OTrule threshold more than 50% to $35,984 on December 1st. https://t.co/3bAvuvOHYK
Last month, I introduced a bill to help curb potential cuts & demotions by phasing in the new #OTrule over 3 years rather than overnight.
Since the new #OTrule was announced, we've heard from employers & employees who are concerned about implementing this increase overnight.
In May, the Department of Labor issued an update to the #OTrule, raising the outdated & inadequate threshold from $23,660 to $47,476.
